Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?M433:=20Fix=20DeslocProgress()=20constructor=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?call=20=E2=80=94=20takes=20no=20args?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

DeslocProgress.__init__(self) accepts no positional arguments.
Call site passed config.max_steps causing TypeError on rank 2.

Signed-off-by: dylanyunlon <dylanyunlong@gmail.com>
---
 REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py b/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py
index b53e3dc..70efcf9 100644
--- a/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py
+++ b/REAL_GPU_BENCHMARK.py
@@ -1777,7 +1777,7 @@ class Trainer:
             self._profiler = get_desloc_profiler()
             # DES-LOC timer from timer.py
             self._stimer = DeslocSTimer()
-            self._progress = DeslocProgress(config.max_steps)
+            self._progress = DeslocProgress()
         else:
             self.engine = None
             self._profiler = None
